00:30:10,759 --> 00:30:11,960
It's too precious to wear.

498
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:13,160
Look, there it is.

499
00:30:13,279 --> 00:30:14,559
I don't want to break it.

500
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:17,400
I don't dare to leave it at home.

501
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,079
I'm afraid that someone will steal it.

502
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:21,480
So I keep it in my handbag every day...

503
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:22,759
and bring it with me.

504
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,400
Seeing it puts me at ease.

505
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,359
It's a necklace.

506
00:30:26,559 --> 00:30:27,559
It won't break easily.

507
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,519
Lu Lu, I need to go to the restroom.

508
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:32,440
I'll go too.

509
00:30:33,319 --> 00:30:34,599
I'm going too!

510
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,680
Come on.

511
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,680
The ladies' room is over there.

512
00:30:54,359 --> 00:30:56,079
Ms. Shi Yi, hold this for me.

513
00:30:56,279 --> 00:30:57,359
I can't.

514
00:31:22,359 --> 00:31:23,640
Bill, please.

515
00:31:34,559 --> 00:31:35,759
Has she come out yet?

516
00:32:22,519 --> 00:32:23,559
I know.

517
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,200
All right.

518
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,039
Sure.

519
00:32:34,519 --> 00:32:35,519
Okay.

520
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,200
Yes.

521
00:32:43,319 --> 00:32:44,400
Let's do that.

522
00:32:49,079 --> 00:32:50,079
Where is the necklace?

523
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,880
Lu Lu, let me ask you.

524
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,039
Where's my necklace?

525
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,039
What's wrong?

526
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,200
I lost my necklace.

527
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,200
Wasn't it in the bag?

528
00:33:02,559 --> 00:33:03,839
That's right.

529
00:33:03,839 --> 00:33:05,000
Where is the necklace?

530
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,519
Did you misplace it?

531
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:10,839
The bag is empty.

532
00:33:11,319 --> 00:33:12,599
I don't know.

533
00:33:13,839 --> 00:33:15,039
- I didn't do anything. - Let me see.

534
00:33:19,079 --> 00:33:20,200
I know.

535
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:21,480
Manager!

536
00:33:22,279 --> 00:33:24,480
- Why are you yelling? - Waiter! Get your manager here!

537
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:25,759
- Hurry up! - No. I'm sorry.

538
00:33:26,279 --> 00:33:27,720
Close the door!

539
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:28,839
No one may enter.

540
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:29,960
What are you doing? Why are you shouting?

541
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:31,680
- Close the door? - I'm looking for a necklace.

542
00:33:31,920 --> 00:33:32,960
Sorry, ma'am.

543
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:34,519
What happened here?

544
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,480
I lost my necklace.

545
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,599
I showed it to you earlier, right?

546
00:33:38,759 --> 00:33:40,200
Then I went to the restroom.

547
00:33:40,519 --> 00:33:41,960
Before I went to the restroom,

548
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:44,279
I left the bag with you.

549
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:48,359
After I came out of the restroom, you returned the bag to me.

550
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:49,680
When I opened the bag,

551
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:50,960
I found that the necklace was gone.

552
00:33:51,079 --> 00:33:52,839
Don't talk nonsense. You must have dropped it somewhere.

553
00:33:52,839 --> 00:33:55,720
I'm not making it up! It's the truth!

554
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,599
- Ma'am, calm down. - How can I not be anxious?

555
00:33:57,599 --> 00:33:58,799
That's an expensive necklace.

556
00:33:58,799 --> 00:34:00,440
It's worth tens of thousands of yuan!

557
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,519
Yes, I know.

558
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:05,519
Since you've lost an item of substantial value,

559
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,279
I'll call the police right away.

560
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,809
Call the police?

561
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,440
Did you drop it somewhere? Look for it.

562
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,880
- Don't create a scene. - I didn't. Call the police.

563
00:34:13,559 --> 00:34:14,639
How about this?

564
00:34:14,809 --> 00:34:17,480
Let's go to my office and wait for the police.

565
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,329
Okay, let's go.

566
00:34:20,119 --> 00:34:21,519
Why bother calling the police and making a scene?

567
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:23,239
Call the police if you want. I'm leaving.

568
00:34:23,559 --> 00:34:25,960
No, you can't go.

569
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:28,920
Hou Jue, I would let it go if anything else is missing.

570
00:34:29,079 --> 00:34:30,519
But it was a gift from you.

571
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:31,809
It's so precious.

572
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:33,159
If you leave now,

573
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:34,809
she will follow you.

574
00:34:34,809 --> 00:34:36,360
She's our prime suspect.

575
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,400
She can't leave.

576
00:34:38,079 --> 00:34:39,159
Fang Lu, I'm warning you.

577
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:41,480
You have no proof to accuse me publicly.

578
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,639
I can sue you for defamation.

579
00:34:43,639 --> 00:34:45,079
Everyone, listen up.

580
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,599
Let's wait in my office.

581
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,289
Okay?

582
00:34:49,289 --> 00:34:50,719
Don't disturb other customers.

583
00:34:51,119 --> 00:34:52,119
Okay?

584
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,000
This way, please.

585
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,039
Come on.

586
00:34:58,239 --> 00:34:59,400
- Excuse me. - What's going on?

587
00:34:59,559 --> 00:35:00,599
We'll take care of it.

588
00:35:00,599 --> 00:35:01,809
Enjoy your meal.

589
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,119
Thank you.

590
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:07,289
When was the last time you saw the necklace?

591
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,440
Where was it?

592
00:35:08,559 --> 00:35:10,329
It was when we were eating.

593
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:12,079
I took the necklace out.

594
00:35:12,079 --> 00:35:13,400
I showed it to Hou Jue.

595
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:14,920
I saw it while we were eating.

596
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:19,239
But I wonder if she was just being careless...

597
00:35:19,239 --> 00:35:20,440
and dropped it when she took it out.

598
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,400
Someone else might have picked it up.

599
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:24,329
Did you go straight into the restroom...

600
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,360
or did you go into the restroom...

601
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,400
after giving it to Wu Shi Yi?

602
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:28,679
Before I went into the restroom,

603
00:35:28,679 --> 00:35:29,960
I gave her the bag.

604
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,289
I suspect it's her.

605
00:35:31,809 --> 00:35:33,199
I'm Hou Jue's security assistant.

606
00:35:33,199 --> 00:35:34,679
Fang Lu did give her bag to me.

607
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:37,440
But she passed it to me after coming out of the restroom.

608
00:35:37,769 --> 00:35:38,920
How long was the process?

609
00:35:39,079 --> 00:35:41,199
- Ms. Shi Yi, hold this for me. - For about 5 to 10 seconds.

610
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,519
Did you touch that bag?

611
00:35:42,519 --> 00:35:43,769
I didn't open it.

612
00:35:43,769 --> 00:35:45,199
I didn't even touch the button.

613
00:35:45,199 --> 00:35:46,239
You may examine the fingerprints.

614
00:35:46,809 --> 00:35:48,159
To avoid suspicion, after I got the bag,

615
00:35:48,159 --> 00:35:49,679
I walked to somewhere with security cameras quickly.

616
00:35:50,239 --> 00:35:51,880
I'm telling you.

617
00:35:52,239 --> 00:35:53,679
Before the surveillance area,

618
00:35:53,679 --> 00:35:54,960
there's a blind spot.

619
00:35:58,639 --> 00:36:00,079
When you went into the restroom,

620
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:02,199
did you see anyone there?

621
00:36:02,599 --> 00:36:04,400
I went to the restroom too.

622
00:36:05,329 --> 00:36:07,289
Besides, whether the ladies' room is empty,

623
00:36:07,289 --> 00:36:08,360
I have no idea.

624
00:36:08,519 --> 00:36:10,920
Yes, a pregnant woman came out of the restroom.

625
00:36:11,289 --> 00:36:13,239
And I noticed that she left very quickly.

626
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:16,809
I needed to go to the restroom badly.

627
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,400
I didn't notice.

628
00:36:19,199 --> 00:36:20,599
I guess not.

629
00:36:20,769 --> 00:36:22,000
That's all for today.

630
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:25,239
If you remember anything, call me anytime.

631
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,119
Thank you.

632
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:30,599
Can I go now?

633
00:36:31,639 --> 00:36:33,079
Okay, Mr. Zhao. I understand.

634
00:36:35,119 --> 00:36:36,119
What's wrong?

635
00:36:36,809 --> 00:36:38,809
Mr. Zhao received a complaint about me.

636
00:36:39,239 --> 00:36:40,599
He demanded that I be recalled immediately.

637
00:36:41,809 --> 00:36:43,000
Who filed a complaint against you?

638
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,039
Did you make the call?

639
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:50,920
It's me.

640
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:52,920
No, it's none of your business.

641
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:54,000
What gives you the right to make this call?

642
00:36:54,809 --> 00:36:55,960
I don't know anything else,

643
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:57,039
but I do know...

644
00:36:57,039 --> 00:36:59,000
that when customers buy a knockoff product,

645
00:36:59,239 --> 00:37:00,519
they can file a complaint.

646
00:37:00,769 --> 00:37:02,119
They can even ask for a refund.

647
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:04,599
You know I have always been a righteous person.

648
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,039
Unlike some people...

649
00:37:06,519 --> 00:37:07,559
who love stealing small things.

650
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:09,809
What are you talking about?

651
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:12,360
What proof do you have...

652
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,360
to prove that Shi Yi did it?

653
00:37:14,079 --> 00:37:16,400
I didn't say that she did it,

654
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,519
but it's proven...

655
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,639
that she is the prime suspect right now.

656
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,719
Hou Jue, you can't let a person like her...

657
00:37:22,719 --> 00:37:23,920
stay by your side anymore.

658
00:37:24,119 --> 00:37:25,329
It makes me worried.

659
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:27,079
It's not up to you to decide whether I keep her or not.

660
00:37:29,289 --> 00:37:30,679
You have to believe me.

661
00:37:30,679 --> 00:37:32,639
Everything I do is for your own good.

662
00:37:32,639 --> 00:37:34,199
If you keep her by your side,

663
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:36,239
you might put yourself in danger.

664
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,519
Shut up.

665
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,880
Shi Yi.

666
00:37:41,039 --> 00:37:42,519
Go and get the car.

667
00:37:42,519 --> 00:37:43,519
Get in.

668
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,159
Come here.

669
00:37:48,159 --> 00:37:49,199
What are you doing?

670
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:51,400
Why did you pull me so forcefully?

671
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,719
You got so mad at me...

672
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,199
over a female bodyguard.

673
00:37:54,199 --> 00:37:55,239
Do you think it's appropriate?

674
00:37:55,239 --> 00:37:56,400
Fang Lu, let me tell you.

675
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,199
I was going to tell you later,

676
00:37:58,199 --> 00:37:59,519
but you left me with no choice.

677
00:38:00,119 --> 00:38:01,199
Let me ask you.

678
00:38:02,119 --> 00:38:04,000
Are you purposely framing Shi Yi?

679
00:38:04,119 --> 00:38:05,440
You didn't lose your necklace, right?

680
00:38:09,289 --> 00:38:11,079
I lost it. I'm not framing her.

681
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,880
I...

682
00:38:13,159 --> 00:38:15,519
Fine, I know you won't admit it.

683
00:38:15,519 --> 00:38:17,199
I don't want to hear you admit it either.

684
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,440
But let me tell you something.

685
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,719
I can't believe...

686
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,559
everything that you say and every expression of yours.

687
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,440
I'm very suspicious, you know?

688
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,769
How could you say that to me?

689
00:38:25,769 --> 00:38:27,119
I'm a victim now.

690
00:38:27,119 --> 00:38:28,599
I'm the one who lost the necklace.

691
00:38:29,159 --> 00:38:30,880
That necklace means a lot to me.

692
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,000
It's not like you don't know.

693
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:33,440
I don't care about anything else.

694
00:38:33,639 --> 00:38:34,679
But...

695
00:38:34,809 --> 00:38:35,920
But that necklace...

696
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:38,119
I'll fight her until the end for it.

697
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:39,360
Why is it even necessary?

698
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:41,719
Hou Jue, I know you have a soft heart.

699
00:38:41,719 --> 00:38:43,840
That's why I called to complain about her.

700
00:38:44,119 --> 00:38:46,440
Anyway, you must not condone this crime.

701
00:38:46,639 --> 00:38:47,769
What do you know?

702
00:38:48,289 --> 00:38:50,079
She's still protecting you.

703
00:38:50,719 --> 00:38:52,719
She said you were having a hard time...

704
00:38:52,719 --> 00:38:54,039
and it must be tough on you.

705
00:38:54,039 --> 00:38:55,719
Who are you to file a complaint against her?

706
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,480
You're so weird.

707
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,639
Shouldn't you be asking me...

708
00:39:00,639 --> 00:39:02,519
why did she do this to me?

709
00:39:04,519 --> 00:39:05,880
I can't seem to knock any sense into you.

710
00:39:06,119 --> 00:39:08,039
What are you saying?

711
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:11,719
Shouldn't you be comforting me now?

712
00:39:12,199 --> 00:39:13,679
Hou Jue!

713
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,360
Go to your company.

714
00:39:20,719 --> 00:39:22,289
I'll talk to Mr. Zhao.

715
00:39:22,289 --> 00:39:24,000
Fang Lu has no right...

716
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,559
to file a complaint against you.

717
00:39:25,559 --> 00:39:26,719
You're my bodyguard.

718
00:39:26,719 --> 00:39:27,960
Why is she complaining about you?

719
00:39:28,289 --> 00:39:29,719
Our company has rules.

720
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,289
We are not allowed to make any mistake in the course of duty.

721
00:39:32,519 --> 00:39:33,920
What rules are these?

722
00:39:34,199 --> 00:39:36,000
Once we make a mistake, we will be recalled immediately...

723
00:39:36,329 --> 00:39:37,519
and await investigation.

724
00:39:38,329 --> 00:39:39,719
Do you know something...

725
00:39:39,719 --> 00:39:40,920
and didn't tell me?

726
00:39:42,289 --> 00:39:44,329
I'm sorry, your private life...

727
00:39:44,329 --> 00:39:45,559
is not part of my job scope.

728
00:39:48,809 --> 00:39:49,840
What do you mean?

729
00:40:00,289 --> 00:40:01,360
Where are you going?

730
00:40:02,329 --> 00:40:03,440
Why did you turn around?

731
00:40:05,039 --> 00:40:06,519
Say something.

732
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:18,960
Why did you come back?

733
00:40:20,239 --> 00:40:22,289
We can't give up on anything that can be a clue.